    "name": "PETRACAL",
    "steam_appid": 3261440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/09aff62c2cabe467d7d95446bce430ea.avif?t=1767387749\" width=501 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After an accident, you find yourself trapped in a labyrinth of narrow tunnels inside a cave. With no room to stand, your only option is to crawl your way toward the exit. In this first-person survival dungeon crawler, death lurks around every corner. Observe, plan and make use of every resource you can find to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/2e02e82981515042a324ddccf50b1531.webp?t=1767387749\" width=276 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are your own compass. To escape, you must chart your surroundings—but remember, every mistake could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/eafeaf1c581793ae5478b11f846cd432.poster.avif?t=1767387749\" width=692 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/eafeaf1c581793ae5478b11f846cd432.webm?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/eafeaf1c581793ae5478b11f846cd432.mp4?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/b85348f66d678b67e549baad2b000504.webp?t=1767387749\" width=383 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your energy, health, and flashlight battery are limited. Use everything wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/b5b7ea1096f0b7150bf0a1fa238a4622.poster.avif?t=1767387749\" width=692 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/b5b7ea1096f0b7150bf0a1fa238a4622.webm?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/b5b7ea1096f0b7150bf0a1fa238a4622.mp4?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/8bd63eb150efffbf6491674bad44c32c.webp?t=1767387749\" width=276 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no way to walk, only crawl. Every bit of energy counts, so move with purpose and plan each movement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/8aa40320bc48ec912fc4838a5126806f.poster.avif?t=1767387749\" width=692 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/8aa40320bc48ec912fc4838a5126806f.webm?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/8aa40320bc48ec912fc4838a5126806f.mp4?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/4b141c56e0212b560ce80aebca568408.webp?t=1767387749\" width=276 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound is your ally. By listening closely, you can detect dangers and uncover opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/cc681ac84ea0138db4d2b9a5f4c1ecd2.poster.avif?t=1767387749\" width=692 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/cc681ac84ea0138db4d2b9a5f4c1ecd2.webm?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/cc681ac84ea0138db4d2b9a5f4c1ecd2.mp4?t=1767387749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/8445a62e288c2d3518a501a43f3e7ced.webp?t=1767387749\" width=276 height=44 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive, claustrophobic environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slow and tense exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement completely limited to crawling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nightmares and dreams.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brutal resource management.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brief experience (it takes one to two hours to complete).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261440/extras/59f49ec15924f84244a3f11f095ec0a7.avif?t=1767387749\" width=501 height=174 /></span></p>",
